(lib/text/news)

NEW COMMANDS AND NEW MUD BEHAVIOR:
---------------------------------
11-16-99 NEW RACES!  Ghost, Ghoul, Drow, and Kender..  Werebeast is being modified
    to allow for multiple differant kinds of beast..  If you wish to change your
    race and have had your character for less then 6 hours then see an Imm.

11-16-99 NEW CLASSES!  Spy, Alchemist, and Guard!

11-16-99 Working on removing levels.  Only levels will be guild and clan levels.

11-16-99 Romance Module is out.  Writing new one.  For now just RP it..

11-16-99 Clan code changed (though not fully implemented).  Clans will be down
    for a little while.  Sorry..

11-16-99 Royal System Changed..  Old Royal (PK system) is dead.  Royalty is now
    based on RPP (role-playing points) and your cities population.  See HELP ROYAL.

11-16-99 Have not updated new in long time..  New channels in.  OOC instead of gossip.
    Tell is only used by newbies and Imms.  RP and emote are working.
    See HELP CHANNELS.

** Royal system is here.  Type HELP ROYAL for more information!!

** Bows, Crossbows, and Slings are now implemented.  Only certian class can use.  Check       your prac to find out if you can.

** AUTOSPLIT, AUTOLOOT, AUTOASSIST ARE IN TYPE AUTO OR TOGGLE TO SEE!

** CLANS ARE HERE! (Only really good for RP right now but later they will do some
   KICK BUTT stuff :)  Start yours now!!)

** Romance modules in type help romance (Doesn't work just yet the help anyway :)  )

** Throw command implemented.  Can be used by ALL (not for long though probably..)

** Type "tnl" to see how much exp till next level!

** Retreat for Thief Class.  Fleeing with no penalty.

** Scrolls of identify now work better.

** Spell abbreviations work (i.e. 'prot f ev' for 'protection from evil').

** Aliases are now in!  Type HELP ALIAS for more information.  Note that    
   aliases are not yet saved when you quit, although they will be in the (very)
   near future.

** Your character no longer gains move points with age.  However, age
   does still affect your HMV gains.  Also, move point modifier objects
   now work correctly.

** You can now use "all" and "all.x" very generally with the get, put,
   drop, junk, donate, give, wear and remove commands.  Type HELP GET
   for more info.

** The "track" function will show you the first step on the shortest
   path to anyone in the game.

** If you drop your link for more than 1 hour, you will be force-rented
   at 25% greater than normal rent prices.  If you don't have enough
   money to rent with, your most valuable items will be junked until
   the money you have can cover your items.

** You can now remove your own messages from the board.  Also, if you
   put someone else's name in parentheses in the message header, they
   will be able to remove the message too.

** The MIDGAARD MAIL SYSTEM is now complete.  The Post Office is north
   of the entrance to the Grunting Boar inn.  Stamps cost 35 coins.

** Fountains have now been implemented.  You can drink from fountains
   or fill containers from fountains using the FILL command.

** The SHOUT command, as always, only reaches people in your zone (you
   can see who these people are by typing WHERE).  The HOLLER command
   reaches everyone in the game.

** When you are writing a message, you will now not be interrupted
   by tells, shouts, emotes, socials, and even people talking in the
   same room.

** The WIMPY command has been upgraded so you can set at how many hit
   points you flee.  Type HELP WIMPY for more info.

*****************************************************************************
    IF YOU LEAVE THE GAME FOR MORE THAN AN HOUR, either by renting or plain
    quitting, your hit points, move points, and mana will be fully restored
    when you come back!  This doesn't work if you're poisoned.
*****************************************************************************

** Use the ASSIST command to engage in mortal combat with someone in the
   room who is getting pummeled.

** Use the SPLIT command to split gold among the members of your group
   (including yourself) who are in the room.  i.e. If you are in a group
   with 4 other people who are in the room with you, type "SPLIT 100"
   to give each of them 20 coins.

** You can use the VISIBLE command to break a spell of invisibility before
   it expires.

